    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/1853a81d6787391bd93de0932328af9d.poster.avif?t=1731618695\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/1853a81d6787391bd93de0932328af9d.webm?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/1853a81d6787391bd93de0932328af9d.mp4?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Shishi：永恒的序曲是一款色彩丰富的地宫探索类角色扮演。身为伊莉雅，一个年轻的魔法师，你将深度探索一座圣所，完成各种挑战并成为一名祭司。<br><br>被女神选择的伊莉雅将展开一场冒险并努力保护王国。不过，她必须先完成训练。伴随着她在永恒圣所的探索，伊莉雅变得更加强大，同时也学习了完成考验所必需的咒语。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >色彩丰富的探索之路！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/b722690b35ddf418009ffe8effc1bd38.poster.avif?t=1731618695\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/b722690b35ddf418009ffe8effc1bd38.webm?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/b722690b35ddf418009ffe8effc1bd38.mp4?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在色彩丰富的地宫探索中与各种生物战斗，并保护好你自己！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在另一个时间线上的约会！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/a0f5941883d40955f3618168952532b7.poster.avif?t=1731618695\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/a0f5941883d40955f3618168952532b7.webm?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/a0f5941883d40955f3618168952532b7.mp4?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每一次探索都在发生在一个新的时间线，也就是说，你将发掘各种各样的房间，遇见新的敌人以及更多内容！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无人能敌的祭司！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/ee0deab002f760c92ba2a2c3f0655917.poster.avif?t=1731618695\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/ee0deab002f760c92ba2a2c3f0655917.webm?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215340/extras/ee0deab002f760c92ba2a2c3f0655917.mp4?t=1731618695\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索、攻击敌人并收集咒语与道具，让大家知道你已准备好去保护这个世界！",
